thread.title: BRIEF-Asymchem Laboratories Tian Jin signs supply agreement with pharmaceutical firm

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Asymchem Laboratories Tian Jin signs supply agreement with pharmaceutical firm

organizations.name: reuters) - asymchem laboratories tian jin co ltd

text:
Jan 24 (Reuters) - Asymchem Laboratories Tian Jin Co Ltd
* Says it signed supply agreement with a pharmaceutical firm on Jan. 23
* Says the pharmaceutical firm will buy pharmaceutical adjunct from the co, with no less than 15 tons in five years
Source text in Chinese: goo.gl/LqMmyK
